solution:
def word_count(text):
    counts = {}
    for word in text.lower().split():
        counts[word] = counts.get(word, 0) + 1
    return counts

test_assertions:
assert word_count('hello world hello') == {'hello':2,'world':1}
assert word_count('The quick brown fox fox fox')['fox'] == 3
